  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcane Archer's gameplay revolves around shooting and detonating explosive arrows to make your way through the game's 12 stages as fast as you can! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/d43b38e44ea84abe7c53ef40bfb8558e.poster.avif?t=1749147591\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/d43b38e44ea84abe7c53ef40bfb8558e.webm?t=1749147591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/d43b38e44ea84abe7c53ef40bfb8558e.mp4?t=1749147591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/ebdb4a2600104e2d558a5e8c25652f9c.poster.avif?t=1749147591\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/ebdb4a2600104e2d558a5e8c25652f9c.webm?t=1749147591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/ebdb4a2600104e2d558a5e8c25652f9c.mp4?t=1749147591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on increasingly difficult levels, and then test your skill against the online leaderboard! Experiment with different strategies and routes  to give yourself an edge! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also features a build-in speedrun timer and level select to help you practice certain levels and become the best archer you can be!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/b487bf147d07803e05990cfcf6973afc.avif?t=1749147591\" width=800 height=448 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcane Archer's gameplay revolves around shooting and detonating explosive arrows to make your way through the game's 12 stages as fast as you can! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/d43b38e44ea84abe7c53ef40bfb8558e.poster.avif?t=1749147591\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/d43b38e44ea84abe7c53ef40bfb8558e.webm?t=1749147591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/d43b38e44ea84abe7c53ef40bfb8558e.mp4?t=1749147591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/ebdb4a2600104e2d558a5e8c25652f9c.poster.avif?t=1749147591\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/ebdb4a2600104e2d558a5e8c25652f9c.webm?t=1749147591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/ebdb4a2600104e2d558a5e8c25652f9c.mp4?t=1749147591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on increasingly difficult levels, and then test your skill against the online leaderboard! Experiment with different strategies and routes  to give yourself an edge! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also features a build-in speedrun timer and level select to help you practice certain levels and become the best archer you can be!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843080/extras/b487bf147d07803e05990cfcf6973afc.avif?t=1749147591\" width=800 height=448 /></span></p>",
